      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes a mechanism for sender-constraining OAuth 2.0 tokens via a proof-of-possession mechanism on the application level.  This mechanism allows for the detection of replay attacks with access and refresh tokens.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
